{"tid":1796931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「和理非最大作用」尋晚平安夜， 證明左人多就係最好既保障","createTime":"2019-12-25T04:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T01:10:19.000Z","uid":11454,"like":106,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd614c23f9741ec549c85c9941207cecc5476f8","tid":1796931,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:17:42.000Z","msg":"先唔好分，市民和理非主動出<br />\n定係純粹平安夜出街慶祝，被當做掩護<br />\n<br />\n見到既係，7-9點依段時間<br />\n基本人多到想走都走唔到<br />\n個個平民行街<br />\n心態無視班狗， 已經係最好既掩護<br />\n手足自己搵位做野<br />\n<br />\n黑警想趕都趕唔走， 唯有鳩拉幾個交數<br />\n<br />\n都後期， 尖沙咀就算有水炮射水， TG放題<br />\n大把「路人」係前面行過<br />\n黑警完全分唔到， 又唔敢強推狗沖<br />\n<br />\n證明心態先係最緊要<br />\n就算和理非， 你要記住， 你只係行街市民<br />\n就算少少TG, 水炮在前， 只要做港豬繼續吃喝玩樂玩， 唔好雞飛狗走<br />\n就係對手足最大既幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然啦， 有節日同紅日放假加持， 人數更多<br />\n但要吸取經驗， 就算平日都應該做一隻「扮豬食老虎」既和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb82f4fe0d981f4a295ed3b2dcee71141cc234a","tid":1796931,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:20:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca6896d746a0d76726dcab4dee56b71bb71dbb94","tid":1796931,"uid":21887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"690a584c7d75eaa3e5e92f7bb650cb1b9f9b9770","tid":1796931,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif